Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku mengerti sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahulu kita di lingkaran kecil terpisah,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi rasanya batasan itu telah hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa masuk UTokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu aku juga bisa akrab dengannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau agak mirip Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat Tani, akhirnya aku\Npaham semuanya di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita baru bahas soal\Nmasuk Universitas Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau beralih cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawabanmu persis seperti Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa otak kalian selaras?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu apa? Malu, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih tidak mengerti?\NYang benar saja, Yamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia kabur karena malu.\N- Ayolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, jam berapa kau pulang hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seperti pelanggan kasar\Nyang menanyakan sif staf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merdeka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bebas sepenuhnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mengganggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya tak ada yang datang\Nsepulang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu menyenangkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo makan sebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau makan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bibinba.\N- Pibinpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani mengucapkannya "pa".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang itu cara pengucapan yang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi "Bibinba" lebih enak di mulut, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo! Bibinba, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki terkadang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, berjuanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian diam-diam membahasku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana asal percaya diri itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku pergi dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mau makan Bibimbap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Aku ingin sekali memakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih suka Bibimbap mangkuk batu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan minta terlalu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang bikin sedikit bersemangat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat toserba
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buka di dekat rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke toserba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantu aku beli tisu toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih murah di toserba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya tersisa sekitar 0,3 gulung lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan pergi begitu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak feminin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}The Exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekalian belikan Lucky Stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pakai baju begini untuk menemui Tani,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mana mungkin aku bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak mungkin, kebetulan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya kupon selebarannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nbukankah itu celana olahraga SMP-mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pakai saat keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya seperti pakaian santai,\Ntapi saat keluar,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pakai celana olahraga bergaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, kau kerja di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan langsung datang di hari pembukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu aku datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau tidak\Ntinggal di dekat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih dekat sekolah,\Njadi lebih mudah kerja di hari kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, jika kerja di dekat rumah,\Nteman-teman SMP-ku akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah bagus jika teman berkunjung?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mengganggu pelanggan lain.\NBisakah cepat pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba jadi pegawai toko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa agak malu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}beli tisu toilet\Ndi tempat kerja teman sekelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang lebih memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa peduli kau malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ambil tiket\Ndan kirim barang lelang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tambah beban kerjaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Es krim rekomendasi Gapacho enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho benar-benar paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa hari ini hujan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujan sedikit di malam hari, lalu berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena baunya mirip udara setelah hujan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tak paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bau rumput dan tanah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa. Maaf, lupakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara motor ganti gigi. Apa itu polisi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari! Lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Nabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang berkendara dan kebetulan lewat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa berkendara kencang di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang paling mungkin tertangkap\Nada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kalian pasangan nakal\Nyang kumpul di dekat pintu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira habislah aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya, itu Suzuki dan Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanku mengira dia dalam masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau berani sekali\Nkeluar pakai baju itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempatnya dekat, apa masalahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai celana olahraga SMP tidak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Tani melihatmu, entah apa pendapatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tidak bisa biarkan\Ndia melihatku begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tak terlalu berbeda dari biasanya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini beda sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani tak akan beli barang\Ndi toserba semalam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada dan Watanabe juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lambat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa keluar semalam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar anak nakal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bersikap seolah itu bukan urusanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Suzuki menghilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat beli barangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki tak pernah ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, setidaknya ejek aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, lari sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelaskan saja padanya nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kembalikan helmku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau jadi diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa tunjukkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau mengecewakanmu\Ndengan terlalu mengekspos diriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, jika aku sudah sejauh ini,\NAkhilles tak akan menyusul si kura-kura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhilles…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau kabur?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau tak melihat banyak perbedaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaanmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Yamada tak keberatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami saling kenal sejak SMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa jika dia melihatku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan Taira dan Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nabe dan aku sudah bersama\Nsejak kelas satu SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Taira,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau jelas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kesal sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau dengar itu\Ndari orang yang jelas melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pandai membantah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya iri Yamada dan yang lain\Nlebih lama mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap saja ada hidangan di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang satu diletakkan di sembarang piring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu lagi ditata dengan hati-hati\Ndi piring cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keduanya terasa sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ingin sajikan yang cantik untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjaga harga diriku!\NIntinya, aku hanya ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli bagaimana penyajiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku suka makanannya,\Naku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu akan menggangguku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat piring dan penyajiannya indah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan orang-orang memuji piring\Natau penyajiannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan lebih bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih bahagia…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, perasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, biarkan aku duduk di belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, tapi aku mungkin tak stabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejuk sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Udara malam musim panas yang sempurna ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau cuacanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini menyenangkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka aroma setelah hujan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Adik Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pulang larut. Pulang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana polisi bisa mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersemangat\Nuntuk kencan festival musim panas kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat bersemangat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah ujian akhir usai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau memutuskan\Npergi ke festival kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk festival kembang api,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami harus cari tempat duduk\Ndan menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu antrean panjang di stasiun setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memikirkannya saja…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat realistis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran\Napa pakai yukata terlalu formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Tentu saja\Nlebih baik pakai yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, tak ada jaminan\Nkalian masih pacaran tahun depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Omong kosong apa itu?\N- Aku hanya bilang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik siapkan mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia melarangmu terlalu pendiam\Nhanya karena kau memacarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan terlalu liar\Nseperti pacar pasangan konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku terlihat aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk menata rambutku?\NHaruskah aku ke salon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana semua orang bisa masukkan\Nbarang ke tas tali sekecil itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sandal karet benar-benar tak lazim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Riasanku mungkin luntur karena keringat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengejutkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini… Ini tidak aneh, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang hanya menyebutku manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa orang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pernah menyebutku cantik?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari menggila di festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak perlu menggila.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini suara dan bau festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari lihat-lihat dahulu,\Nlalu putuskan mau beli apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan jika ada stan\Nyang ingin kau kunjungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, di belakangmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini ramai, kita harus berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini benar-benar terasa\Nseolah kita pasangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, aku terlalu bersemangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kami bertemu setiap hari di sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu sebabnya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}momen seperti ini
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mau bagi dua?\N- Tidak baik
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hore!\N- jika terlalu bersemangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lezat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh tak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan keadaan sekarang…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak mungkin…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak bersemangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin aku boleh minta satu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kau boleh ambil keduanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika butuh sesuatu untuk lap tangan,\Nberi tahu saja aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sudah memikirkan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua kemungkinan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah lebih cerdas\Njika tidak mengatakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara yang gila untuk bermesraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah yang terjadi\Nsaat kau di puncak kegembiraan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi yang paling membuatku takut adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa memahami perasaan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat tak punya pacar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anehnya aku yakin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak akan terlalu bersemangat\Nsampai lupa diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa aku hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?\NTiba-tiba aku merasa sangat malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, sudah waktunya kau pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, mau jalan denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah ke sekitar sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mulai menanjak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia membawaku ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah untuk melihat pemandangan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sampai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini agak canggung…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu niatnya,\Njadi sulit meresponsnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembang apinya belum mulai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar lagi. Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini festival kembang api\Nyang tak kita datangi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya terlihat dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah apa bisa memotretnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cukup jauh, jadi kurasa tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, rekam dengan mata saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kami akan berciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kami tidak berciuman…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku ingin menciumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari menonton di dekat sini lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali? Di dekat sini? Menonton apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahun depan juga ada, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Ayo kita pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bagian dari "tahun depan" Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menikmati festivalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menang besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menang apa?
